channel.title: My server Accomplishments
channel.description:
Hello METAL here with my second post,
Hello I've been working on my server for quite some time now. I've went through error upon errors, I started with a blank original Moparscape server with no NPC's not even bankers. I worked and worked on my server till Miss Silabsoft released her client with the newer items I'm currently Looking for a [377] server to work on if you have any suggestions read my first post (link at the bottom.)
[b]-Finished Working on- - 15+ shops all with different items ( A weird goal I had.) - Added newest items. - 100% working wilderness levels. - NPC's in the right places. - My own dueling arena (That's right i have a a custom duel arena (not saying where.) - 63 wave fire cape mini. - And much, much more. - 100% working specials ( who doesn't have this goal.) - 100% working lunar (I've got all but 3 spells working.) - And other projects on working on[/b]
Link to my other post I was talking about : http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,357832.0.html
